1. Imamo *potrebu* za novim računarom. (We have a *need* for a new computer.)
2. Njihova *potreba* za hranom bila je velika nakon dugog putovanja. (Their *need* for food was great after a long journey.)
3. Ured treba da osigura osnovne *potrebe* svojih zaposlenih. (The office needs to provide basic *needs* for its employees.)
4. *Potrebno* je da se pridržavate pravila u ovom prostoru. (It is *necessary* to follow the rules in this area.)
5. Zadovoljavanje *potreba* klijenata je prioritet našeg poslovanja. (Satisfying the *needs* of clients is our business priority.)
6. Ona je *potrebna* našoj zajednici zbog svog znanja i iskustva. (She is *needed* in our community because of her knowledge and experience.)
7. Koliko *potrebe* za novcem imate ovog meseca? (How much *need* for money do you have this month?)
8. Da bismo rešili ovaj problem, *potrebno* nam je više vremena. (To solve this problem, we *need* more time.)
9. Društvo ima *potrebu* da osigura pravdu i jednakost za sve svoje građane. (Society has a *need* to ensure justice and equality for all its citizens.)
10. Ako želite da uspete u ovom poslu, *potrebno* je da budete uporni i istrajni. (If you want to succeed in this business, it is *necessary* to be persistent and persevering.)